"title": "5499: reward, divine",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "5499: reward, divine",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>God's dealings with people are always in harmony with his grace and his justice, hating evil and loving good. No gift of God is on the basis of merit, but on the basis of his faithfulness to his promises.</p>\n<h2>God's reward is in harmony with his character</h2>\n<h3>His graciousness</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom4:4-Rom4:5\">ROM 4:4–4:5</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps103:10\">PSA 103:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt20:14-Matt20:15\">MAT 20:14–20:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke17:7-Luke17:10\">LUK 17:7–17:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom11:6-Rom11:7\">ROM 11:6–11:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph2:8-Eph2:10\">EPH 2:8–2:10</a></p>\n<h3>His justice</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom2:6-Rom2:11\">ROM 2:6–2:11</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut28:1-Deut28:2\">DEU 28:1–28:2</a> <em>blessings for obedience</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut28:15\">DEU 28:15</a> <em>curses for disobedience</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps19:9-Ps19:11\">PSA 19:9–19:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps62:12\">PSA 62:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov13:21\">PRO 13:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov14:14\">PRO 14:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer17:10\">JER 17:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer32:19\">JER 32:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor3:8\">1CO 3:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor9:6\">2CO 9:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal6:7-Gal6:9\">GAL 6:7–6:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph6:8\">EPH 6:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col3:25\">COL 3:25</a></p>\n<h2>The reward of the ungodly</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom6:23\">ROM 6:23</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod20:5\">EXO 20:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut7:9-Deut7:10\">DEU 7:9–7:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov22:22-Prov22:23\">PRO 22:22–22:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa13:11\">ISA 13:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa26:21\">ISA 26:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa59:18\">ISA 59:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa65:6-Isa65:7\">ISA 65:6–65:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa66:6\">ISA 66:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek7:4\">EZK 7:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek9:10\">EZK 9:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek11:21\">EZK 11:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos9:7\">HOS 9:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zeph1:12\">ZEP 1:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Thess1:6\">2TH 1:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb2:1-Heb2:2\">HEB 2:1–2:2</a></p>\n<h2>The reward of the godly</h2>\n<h3>God's treatment of the righteous</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:17-Rom8:18\">ROM 8:17–8:18</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod19:5\">EXO 19:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ruth2:12\">RUT 2:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam22:25\">2SA 22:25</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps18:20\">PSA 18:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps18:24\">PSA 18:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs3:14\">1KI 3:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr15:7\">2CH 15:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps19:9-Ps19:11\">PSA 19:9–19:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps58:11\">PSA 58:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov11:18\">PRO 11:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov11:28\">PRO 11:28</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov13:21\">PRO 13:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov19:17\">PRO 19:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov31:31\">PRO 31:31</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa62:10-Isa62:12\">ISA 62:10–62:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer31:16\">JER 31:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt5:12\">MAT 5:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke6:34-Luke6:35\">LUK 6:34–6:35</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor2:9-1Cor2:10\">1CO 2:9–2:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas1:25\">JAS 1:25</a></p>\n<h3>The example of Jesus Christ</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil2:8-Phil2:11\">PHP 2:8–2:11</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb12:2-Heb12:3\">HEB 12:2–12:3</a></p>\n<h3>Apparent unfair treatment of the godly</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps73:13-Ps73:14\">PSA 73:13–73:14</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job1:1\">JOB 1:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job2:11-Job2:13\">JOB 2:11–2:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job9:29-Job9:31\">JOB 9:29–9:31</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa49:4\">ISA 49:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hab1:12-Hab1:13\">HAB 1:12–1:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt5:10\">MAT 5:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim3:12\">2TI 3:12</a></p>",
